<h4><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/TGu1hUy2R4C1Vbham6p1mg">郭明錤：iPhone 13 Pro 或升级超广角相机</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1377568" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Apple_announce-iphone12pro_10132020.jpg.landing-big_2x.jpg" alt="" width="1312" height="738" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Apple_announce-iphone12pro_10132020.jpg.landing-big_2x.jpg 1312w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Apple_announce-iphone12pro_10132020.jpg.landing-big_2x-360x203.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Apple_announce-iphone12pro_10132020.jpg.landing-big_2x-768x432.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Apple_announce-iphone12pro_10132020.jpg.landing-big_2x-1024x576.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1312px) 100vw, 1312px" /></p>
<p>天风国际消息，分析师郭明錤预测，在将于 2021 年下半年发布的新款 iPhone 中，两款高端机型的超广角相机将升级至 f/1.8、6P 和自动对焦。</p>
<p>郭明錤预测，所有在 2022 年下半年推出的新款 iPhone 都将配备 f/1.8、6P 和自动对焦的超广角相机。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.engadget.com/fda-approves-apple-watch-nightmare-app-205016585.html">FDA 批准了一款可干预噩梦的 Apple Watch 应用</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1377569" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/dims.jpeg" alt="" width="1600" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/dims.jpeg 1600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/dims-360x180.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/dims-768x384.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/dims-1024x512.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /></p>
<p>Engadget 消息，美国食品药品管理局（FDA）批准了一款名为 NightWare 的应用。该应用声称可协作干预由类似 PTSD 等障碍引起的噩梦。</p>
<p>NightWare 通过收集分析心率等体征数据，在不至于唤醒用户的情况下，适当地振动以干预噩梦。目前，NightWare 为「处方应用」，该公司也强调应用只是整体治疗的一部分。</p>
<h4><a href="https://new.qq.com/rain/a/20201108A06MYL00">我国数学家证明微分几何学两大核心猜想</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1377570" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6a54-kcpxnww5691854.jpg" alt="" width="720" height="380" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6a54-kcpxnww5691854.jpg 720w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6a54-kcpxnww5691854-360x190.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" /></p>
<p>新华社消息，中国科学技术大学教授陈秀雄、王兵在微分几何学领域取得重大突破，成功证明了「哈密尔顿 &#8211; 田」和「偏零阶估计」这两个国际数学界 20 多年悬而未决的核心猜想。</p>
<p>日前，国际顶级数学期刊《微分几何学杂志》发表了这一成果，论文篇幅超过 120 页，从写作到发表历时 11 年。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293889" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.pingwest.com/w/222226">三星 S21 系列或不赠有线耳机</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1377571" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/The-Samsung-Galaxy-S21-will-be-a-major-leap-in-smartphone-design-if-rumors-are-correct.jpg" alt="" width="1600" height="1067" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/The-Samsung-Galaxy-S21-will-be-a-major-leap-in-smartphone-design-if-rumors-are-correct.jpg 1600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/The-Samsung-Galaxy-S21-will-be-a-major-leap-in-smartphone-design-if-rumors-are-correct-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/The-Samsung-Galaxy-S21-will-be-a-major-leap-in-smartphone-design-if-rumors-are-correct-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/The-Samsung-Galaxy-S21-will-be-a-major-leap-in-smartphone-design-if-rumors-are-correct-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px" /></p>
<p>品玩援引韩媒《Top Daily》消息指出，三星正在考虑取消将于 2021 年初发布的三星 Galaxy S21 系列的部分赠送配件。</p>
<p>其中，有很高机率三星将不再赠送 AKG 有线耳机。此前三星 Galaxy Note20 先前在美国地区上市时，就取消附赠耳机，消费者需要与官方客服沟通后才能获得有线耳机。同时，三星打算将即将发布的无线耳机 Galaxy Buds Beyond 与 S21 系列一同捆绑销售。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-11-06/apple-sony-said-to-hold-talks-about-buying-podcaster-wondery">传苹果和索尼在竞购播客公司 Wondery</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1377572" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/364997886.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="697" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/364997886.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/364997886-360x209.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/364997886-768x446.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/364997886-1024x595.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>《彭博社》援引知情人士消息称，苹果和索尼音乐都分别在和播客公司 Wondery 洽谈收购事宜，两家公司为目前至少四家在商谈收购的公司。</p>
<p>Wondery 是其中一家最大的独立播客公司，拥有一系列可改编为电视剧的播客，触达的听众月活约为 800 万人。消息人士称 Wondery 在寻求价值 3-4 亿美元的出售。</p>
<p>苹果过去曾至少收购了两家小播客公司。而索尼音乐则是全球三大音乐公司中收购最多播客相关公司的企业。</p>
<h4>B 站首届「CHINA-Z 100」年度十大产品出炉</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1377573" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/bzhan.jpg" alt="" width="1138" height="683" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/bzhan.jpg 1138w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/bzhan-360x216.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/bzhan-768x461.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/bzhan-1024x615.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1138px) 100vw, 1138px" /></p>
<p>昨晚，哔哩哔哩公布了首届「China-Z 100」榜单，揭晓了最受年轻人喜爱的十大中国产品。</p>
<p>卫龙大面筋、元气森林燃茶、友基 EXRAI pro 16 位数位屏、2020 狼人杀限定版卡牌、极米 Z6X 投影仪、小米米家空气净化器 Pro、Girlcult 屁桃联名腮红、毛戈平光感滋润无痕粉膏、华为 P40 及大疆御 Mavic Mini 航拍小飞机，荣获 B 站十大年轻人喜爱的中国产品称号。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357461" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/citylife-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4><a href="https://www.businessinsider.com/ikea-partnered-tiny-home-maker-unveil-its-tiny-home-project-2020-11">宜家推出带轮子的迷你住宅</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1377575" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5fa1735e69331a0011bc6f00.jpeg" alt="" width="1920" height="1440" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5fa1735e69331a0011bc6f00.jpeg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5fa1735e69331a0011bc6f00-360x270.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5fa1735e69331a0011bc6f00-768x576.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5fa1735e69331a0011bc6f00-1024x768.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>《Business Insider》消息，宜家和专注迷你住宅的 Escape Homes 合作，打造了一款带轮子的迷你住宅。</p>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1377576" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5fa174af1df1d5001821884e.jpeg" alt="" width="600" height="450" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5fa174af1df1d5001821884e.jpeg 600w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5fa174af1df1d5001821884e-360x270.jpeg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></p>
<p>这个迷你住宅占地面积为 187 平方英尺（约 17.37 平米），包括了一个睡房、起居室、厨房和洗手间，室内配置了宜家的家居产品，定价 63350 美元（约人民币 42 万元）。</p>
<h4><a href="https://www.yahoo.com/lifestyle/meet-sethunya-louis-vuitton-549-000131311.html?guccounter=1&amp;guce_referrer=aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbS8&amp;guce_referrer_sig=AQAAABpBZxyOcprpIacePmm2Faj43p9T5bcHA_65g7qzXtGLl--lbY1Yyjb4tr5lr-70Lsj7-drz_Zrjkub22Quh-0VW_KLjjQq15U3B9ZqbT6m0Oyx_db9LwO61rVBXH_N0ROttdAycb2ekcK0QpWGNI2pUMdhnyRaKJfJHCi_xZBth">LV 获得一枚巨型钻石原石</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1377577" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/a173487294048fce23942054427e1f02.png" alt="" width="959" height="776" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/a173487294048fce23942054427e1f02.png 959w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/a173487294048fce23942054427e1f02-360x291.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/a173487294048fce23942054427e1f02-768x621.png 768w" sizes="(max-width: 959px) 100vw, 959px" /></p>
<p>Louis Vuitton 宣布获得了一枚重达 549 克拉的钻石原石，并联手客户将其打造为独特的作品。LV 将其命名为「Sethunya」，意为塞斯瓦纳语中的「花」，呼应了品牌标志性的 Monogram 印花图案。</p>
<p>该原石虽然小于 LV 去年获得的另一枚 1758 克拉的钻石原石，但其净度更高。预计形成于 10-20 亿年前。目前，全球最大钻石原石是 1905 年开采出来的「Cullinan」，重量为 3106 克拉。</p>
<h4><a href="https://hypebeast.cn/2020/11/citizen-beams-ana-digi-temps-watch-release">BEAMS x Citizen 推出合作表款 ANA-DIGI TEMP</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1377578" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/watech.jpg" alt="" width="1200" height="680" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/watech.jpg 1200w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/watech-360x204.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/watech-768x435.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/watech-1024x580.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px" /></p>
<p>Hypebeast 消息，Citizen 与 BEAMS 基于经典方型表款，打造了 ANA-DIGI TEMP。</p>
<p>值得指出的是，虽然合作款造型复古，但表盘上的数字等信息却采用了手写体字体，让整体设计更亲和。</p>
<h4><a href="http://news.mtime.com/2020/11/07/1604629.html">科林·费斯将出演国漫改编电影《尸兄》</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1377579" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/poster-1.jpg" alt="" width="1547" height="1109" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/poster-1.jpg 1547w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/poster-1-360x258.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/poster-1-768x551.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/poster-1-1024x734.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1547px) 100vw, 1547px" /></p>
<p>时光网消息，有报道称科林・费斯将加盟中国动漫《尸兄》改编的好莱坞真人电影。费斯出演角色暂未公布，据说是一个「能让他玩得开心，又能展示他的冷面幽默和漫画时刻」的角色。</p>
<p>《尸兄》电影版英文名暂定《纽约将会生吞你 (New York Will Eat You Alive)》，类型为另类丧尸动作喜剧片。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293890" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/wangyo-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4>潍坊高新区禁止让家长批改作业</h4>
<p>山东潍坊市教育局高新分局出台《潍坊高新区学生作业规范「十要十不」》，明确：① 小学一二年级不得布置书面作业；② 不得让家长或变相由家长打印作业；③ 不得出现要求家长代批阅作业现象；④ 周一到周五不得安排学生带回家中完成实践类作业。 ​​​​</p>
<p>网友：「批改作业本来就是老师的工作，家长的职责是监督好自己孩子完成作业。」「一二年级不布置书面作业，那三年级后能适应么？」「仿佛已经看到了教育机构在笑。」</p>
<h1><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1357402" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/mon.png" alt="" width="1029" height="153" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/mon.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/mon-360x54.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/mon-768x114.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/mon-1024x152.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h1>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1377512" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/s33663376.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="800" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/s33663376.jpg 800w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/s33663376-360x360.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/s33663376-768x768.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>书名：《椅子与身体》</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>作者：[日] 黑川雅之</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>页数：152</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong>出版时间：2020 年 7 月</strong></p>
<p>很多建筑师在人生中都会设计一把椅子，究其原因，是因为椅子能够体现建筑师的哲学。</p>
<p>为什么人要坐在椅子上？黑川雅之认为，椅子不仅仅是为了休息而坐的存在，人类是为了创造而坐在椅子上的。人类是什么？人体又是什么？在本书中，黑川雅之指出，只有了解了人本身，才会更好地了解椅子的构造。而反过来悟透了椅子的设计，才能更深刻地了解人类本身。</p>
